<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<title>HOUSE OF KILLING</title>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
		<!-- <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="archivestyle.css"> -->
		<style>
			body{
				background-color: blue;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				margin:0;
				padding:0;
			}
			.headline{
				color: rgba(0,0,0,0);
     			-webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(0,0,0,0); /* Will override color (regardless of order) */
     			-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1px;
     			-webkit-text-stroke-color: white;
				font-family: sans-serif;
				font-size: 50px;
				margin:10px;
				padding:0;
				font-style: italic;
			}
			.smaller{
				-webkit-text-fill-color: white;
				-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0;
				font-size: 20px;
				font-weight: 100;
			}
			.paragraph{
				color: white;
				margin:10px;
				font-size: 12px;
				max-width: 40%;
				font-style: italic;
			}

			#waitingroom{
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				position: fixed;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				right: 0;
				bottom: 0;
				display: inline-block;
				z-index: 9;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				justify-content: space-evenly;

			}
			#roomregistration{
				width: 100%;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: row;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
			}
			#lounge{
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				justify-content: flex-end;
				border: 2px solid blue;
				margin: 10px;
			}
			#room-id{
				font-size: 30px;
				text-align: left;
				margin-left:10px;
				font-size: 12px;
				color: white;
				background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);
				border: 0;
				border-bottom: 1px white solid;
				width:50%;
			}
			#lounge{
				display: none;
			}
			#buttons{
				display: flex;
				white-space: nowrap;
			}
			button{
				border: 1px white solid;
				font-size: 12px;
				margin-right: 10px;
			}
			button:focus{
				decoration: none;
				outline: none;
			}
			#container{
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: row;
				justify-content: left
				flex-wrap: wrap;

			}
			video{
				width: 100%;
			}
			.videoelement{
				width: 30%;
			}
			#blocker {
			display: none;
				z-index: 0;
			  position: fixed;
			  left: 0;
			  top: 0;
			  width: 100%;
			  height: 100%;
			  background-color: rgba(0,20,200,0.5);
			}
			.play{
				position: relative;
				top: 50%;
			}

			#instructions {
				display: none;
			  width: 70%;
			  height: 50%;
			  position: fixed;
			  left: 50%;
			  top: 20%;
			  transform: translateX(-50%);
			  color: white;
			  background-color: rgba(0,20,200,0.5);
			  text-align: center;
			  font-family: Arial;
			  font-size: 1vw;
			  line-height: auto;
			  cursor: pointer;
			}
			.headlines {
	          white-space: nowrap;
	          position: absolute;
	          z-index: 8;
	          font-family: "friends";
	          left: 0;
	        }

	        a {
	          text-decoration: none;
	          color: white;
			  font-size: 40px
	        }

	        a:hover {
	          color: yellow;
	          text-decoration: underline;

	        }


	        .ticker {
	          position: relative;
	          overflow: hidden;
	          height: 50px;

	        }
			.toggle{
				position: fixed;
				right:0;
				bottom: 0;
				margin: 10px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
        <!-- <video id="video" class="video" autoplay></video> -->
		<div id="blocker">
			<div id="instructions">
				<h1 class="headline"><small class="smaller">welcome to the <br/></small>WEBCAM LANDSCAPEâ„¢<br/></h1>


				Move: WASD<br/>
				Jump: SPACE<br/>
				Look: MOUSE<br/>
                escape: ESC
				<br /><br />
				<span class="play headline">Click to play</span>

			</div>

		</div>

		<div id="waitingroom">
			<h1 class="headline">HOUSE OF KILLING <br> studio, presents <br><small class="smaller">a gamefied 3D livestreaming concept</small></h1>
			<h1 class="headline cursive">BETA </h1>
			<p class="paragraph">{this is a beta deployment  of 3D livestreaming concept. It renders you and your e-friends on 3D shapes in a gamified 3D environment.<br>
				{to try it, open a room below, by creating a new room-name and clicking "create room", or by joining an e-friends room by typing their room-name and clicking "join room"}}{when you and your e-friends have all collected here on this page, click "go 3D", and go gaming}</p>
			<div id="roomregistration">
			  <input
				type="text"
				id="room-id"
				value="create or input room-id"
				autocorrect="off"
				autocapitalize="off"
				size="20"
			  />
			<div id="buttons">
				<button id="btn-open-room">Open Room</button>
				<button id="btn-join-room">Join Room</button>
			</div>
			</div>
			<div id="lounge">
				<div id="container"></div>
				<button id="3d-toggle" class="toggle">go 3D</button>
			</div>

		</div>








